{"tid":1843112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［必睇］抵抗武漢肺炎五寶","createTime":"2020-01-26T05:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T11:17:10.000Z","uid":18577,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9dedfd830ce803a71e8a54a03d1c4f00115be00","tid":1843112,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"知道好多連登巴絲都好緊張<br />\n但都想提提各位一次<br />\n襯住依家應該重有存貨（口罩除外）<br />\n買齊依五樣野擺屋企<br />\n<br />\n1. 口罩<br />\n大家上網代購啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HndKCjr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHndKCjr.jpg&h=5fc36359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 漂白水<br />\n見到hktvmall 重有得賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ncBzZxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FncBzZxW.jpg&h=dbba766a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漂白水要點用呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyumEx5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyumEx5.jpg&h=95c7426e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 酒精搓手液<br />\n一定要帶黎旁身<br />\n建議大家買枝大嘅放屋企方便refill<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJjaxTo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJjaxTo.jpg&h=30580002&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Tk1Eyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Tk1Eyp.jpg&h=6a71736b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.火酒<br />\n如果屋企用地毯記住一定要噴火酒<br />\n本身係屋企都噴下啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o6hze7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo6hze7b.jpg&h=f5e8689d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.消毒紙巾<br />\n捰黎抹電話又好..抹乜都好啦<br />\n比埋你地睇買邊隻好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ud14CkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fud14CkM.jpg&h=fb24ef2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tAsfJ0N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtAsfJ0N.jpg&h=b66d48b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後send依幅圖比身邊嘅人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xAkU7F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xAkU7F.png&h=b96cddb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝各位身體健康</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港大罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"af8533c217802611c6e4a4781953e838522bc2c9","tid":1843112,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0d41f045e36dfd57f37c7c2c6f88f1e916bc47","tid":1843112,"uid":24227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"大佬咪撚買曬d alcohol pads<br />\n好多病人打釘督手指要用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4d42fafa11846fcb39107e3f1536f0e0b49b7b","tid":1843112,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"有用post <br />\n批准永久置頂"},{"pid":"285e967d0d4e479e430af242dce7a2365187c4e5","tid":1843112,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:19:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大佬咪撚買曬d alcohol pads<br />\n好多病人打<span style=\"color: red;\">針</span>督手指要用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aa2ea6f84e3d8